goal.tools.unittest.result

Class UnitTestResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • goal.tools.unittest.result.UnitTestResult

  • public class UnitTestResult
extends java.lang.Object
    The results of executing a UnitTest. A UnitTest can be ran using RunTest. Because the UnitTest starts a MAS and binds AgentTests to agents using their base name there may be multiple AgentTestResults for a test. Likewise there may be agents that ran but did not have an associated test. A Unit test is considered to be passed if all UnitTestInterpreterResults are passed and if for each AgentTest defined in the UnitTest there is at least one result.
    Author:
    M.P. Korstanje
